{"type":"message","id":"17f482bf","parentId":"4f229b1d","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:54:16.150Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Researching financial metrics**\n\nI want to gather sector info, historical data, and financial metrics. For a deeper analysis, I'll need to look into valuation, trends, and risks. Python will help me collect this data. My goal is to create a concise research summary with details like current price, recent highs/lows, moving averages, volume, and revenue/net profit growth. The stock_individual_info_em function can help provide totals and ratios, and I'll also check fund flows using stock_individual_fund_flow. Let's inspect the function requirements.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0142f9a21f5351e00169c491c1cb4c819bbf41bfee4d891f9a\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpxJHGoZh1qiw4V53jOr0OOm5-Zb65Inh00KElcG6Bh8b29xWsfk4ZTA_YLdudd3HrEBSOjab_R2sg-d1-z7KCt5u_pGN97Wc4cYmlc7uTFBlaQ8uKn84sNzS050kopbaRGuPhl0GwNjwCSFWXFziIyppJCMC-8wjjoXRU-_CCSFeT_Yr1FQ2aIuzprCddly8lvJZ_6HlfibX6RKrZ0Z-pJy2SMn55Gc1hvmWAH5oG73wUGvaezTFXj0lGkKEJJREJqiEE4qOl5WDgUreOY3OQtxjhK4gGyt09wetBepg4J3LTF6Kmynlou1TvtrWh70sM_Ki_nXSYVWptY23SAFC85tG_3P47CWG6yz3EVcNcNd6CbU7_qqy_hmnxIoT8Z1OhMitcCc8MMc-tykYRh2d6AGHtbcxlgEmgKiP4vOSu7TiEDc8n27lQvMWw_Qzz8rUDWfVBP1u5HJUuTCHZOLoJGTSHHVA756rWVJhwPE0uucBDU8NOq26i6IMoiwek3EzyaLxiwMzPfMPIJ-lolSSYOO446502ydmk_G65nhg9iNBbP1JaIfl58fyj9N3S48EbKopTG1kwM1lcZKinim0JC9_dUlgFHUqGbMDK4Net_MS7VKfp57tyd37aJQKQU9sip2iYoAwM5lS2CRgHo6GzTqzYpe4-5jbY-YztLpoDeAdcCcy6wf8KT048xt2Iu5ODMg95LFOSWAVrGUUsJ3acIgfop6fZqQ6ye8WYPweV-aBi3f-FIKPTQXXuWWp6-WA_NakMO_K3V03lQpwfMiBZ_MMiYv0tFvN0GvmClUCYJ1yCmi9jNZPZAKlU2PcB5DsnBM1tGWBKgNyR_oKoBAPQmNMmCIywPIY54G9DQuiQqMDNqu8WDCSPvkMQGhoZ_mgEnU6cORMvzFG5a0QTgTMo5-NKTEH9JcFEOzGkTlLj5zCoqHgs7RLnBXKplSqX1k6BTkcQbZwhNUc18e5Kkg5c4fZkwLqzhFUXbLGg84AhKCSBSakDWj72NGz-vsl6hWvabFY46H_aSPzIKNGgT2Wwc8zwjSK_ntEvnzgh_NWNZ6hsUO1ipiPuu5Lh4UQ77ZXJCEQQm9f1QgpSy9syudaevY9x-UI1HZRRcM9UE0HuP4eC