{"type":"message","id":"786bbf16","parentId":"3121116b","timestamp":"2026-03-26T04:04:24.486Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5I4ScWw9VjCLR7qwB2sxEIk8|fc_0142f9a21f5351e00169c4b0481b64819ba9ba4e85bd548d29","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# 健身计划提醒脚本\n# 每天 11:30 推送\n\nDAY=$(date +%u)  # 1=周一, 2=周二, ...\n\ncase $DAY in\n  1) PLAN=\"周一：背部雕刻与呼吸校准\n• 死虫式 4组×16次\n• 单臂哑铃划船 4组×12次/侧\n• 仰卧哑铃Pullover 3组×12次\n• 有氧：划船机30分钟\" ;;\n  2) PLAN=\"周二：下肢后侧日\n• 哑铃罗马尼亚硬拉 4组×12次\n• 负重臀桥 4组×15次\n• 鸟狗式 3组×12次/侧\n• 有氧：椭圆机30分钟\" ;;\n  3) PLAN=\"周三：胸肩塑形与核心\n• 哑铃平卧推胸 4组×12次\n• 哑铃侧平举 4组×15次\n• 死虫式 4组×16次\n• 有氧：划船机30分钟\" ;;\n  4) PLAN=\"周四：下肢前侧日\n• 哑铃箱式深蹲 4组×12次\n• 靠墙静蹲 3组×60秒\n• 侧卧抬腿 3组×20次/侧\n• 有氧：椭圆机30分钟\" ;;\n  5) PLAN=\"周五：全身高效代谢日\n• 循环模式：硬拉→划船→推胸 各12次 ×4轮\n• 有氧：划船机30分钟\" ;;\n  6) PLAN=\"周六：休息日\n• 可以轻松散步或瑜伽拉伸\" ;;\n  7) PLAN=\"周日：休息日\n• 建议使用筋膜枪放松全身\" ;;\nesac\n\nMESSAGE=\"🧘 精英减脂增肌 - $(date +%m月%d日)\n\n⏰ 12:00-13:30 课程表\n\n$PLAN\n\n🥗 练后补给（14:00前）：\n• 碳水：120-150g蒸紫薯\n• 蛋白：180g 牛肉/虾肉/鸡肉\n• 蔬菜：多样化\n• 补剂：维生素D3\n\n⚠️ 心率红线：绝不上180，感觉不适立刻停下！\"\n\n# 发送到飞书（通过OpenClaw消息）\necho \"$MESSAGE\"\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774497864474}}
{"type":"message","id":"5a4dc880","parentId":"786bbf16","timestamp":"2026-03-26T04:04:24.503Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_jVgT7E68WzdRFCXtly5YB1hW|fc_0142f9a21f5351e00169c4b0481b74819b8cec678a658b9e8d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 定时任务配置\n# 运行 crontab -e 并添加以下行:\n\n# 每日盘前新闻分析 (8:50, 交易日)\n50 8 * * 1-5 /usr/bin/python3 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/daily_market_report.py >> /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/logs/daily_market_report.log 2>&1\n\n# 每日早盘 (9:00, 交易日)\n0 9 * * 1-5 /usr/bin/python3 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/morning_scan.py >> /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/logs/morning.log 2>&1\n\n# 每日午后 (14:00, 交易日)\n0 14 * * 1-5 /usr/bin/python3 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/afternoon_check.py >> /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/logs/afternoon.log 2>&1\n\n# 每周优化 (周五 20:00)\n0 20 * * 5 /usr/bin/python3 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/weekly_optimize.py >> /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/logs/weekly.log 2>&1\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774497864486}}
