{"type":"message","id":"595f237d","parentId":"a08fa4be","timestamp":"2026-03-26T04:12:11.696Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Verifying task transitions**\n\nI need to ensure I'm using active_task_cli to show the verify state and advance through all transitions. Since there's a priority change, I should overwrite ACTIVE_TASK.md before I do any substantial work. It might help to use a full-file write to rebuild the file, then read it back. The instructions say to overwrite it clearly when priority changes. I'll check out the script and the template to make sure everything aligns well.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0142f9a21f5351e00169c4b211b39c819ba43b319531e99d1c\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpxLIboeHXJG-W3opk_U1mVIYvCK-XlgQr-2thQ4K5gRFzoFMXnufxMHmX0ctgKKjxWjF1cXe1K96wQj3FTLwPntHzt0upmfx0YFc4UKu3jiwZtMnXxR_ZV-Yc5AeA-2qs6GGeB81CG7YbyGy0bMo6SVBCArhLlGWB028dGIWB3Gd-WBYqPN0LRa1CMMnmTfnrf5vNahseQRtoHNtbQAWAWoHll1ircJAyzO3UH63pWsHv1OZJ1cjiEcbVcAvajMM-BB1-PCF4wuuiGkD89Fz1iZUS0JApr8om3nuUIjeT7TKJGZJ8WhyrWQuwHyovrIa9VsCTqt5yYDDFb50sKEMsT95j7wZNS8DEdZKOOPRCDBDtqGMMCHi0f1_3sR30ZXUNou3z6k_COZc8Inwmda9hy0JoW6lTaWdMq6PJMZCwwdjpCg3zKRGpR8KroAMmNRRx77VyRtUZ4N31d9Ty1uraX504ssEf5BgWdITgmgSzZf-eHWDOgSEJWHw_Cwxxfyl-e7AWTC5_WYEYkp0MJi-ArCiGOwb5Ag8aLtU27arcFWQnO_mAAEjtrrf9ORKuigK-T1IYS4635-bxyCuRqJYX7GLMEXGTHIVhOm5cFVyAGVCUFeKuDawcKAgYbhDYdwbcGj2V8JWnXmyoOE4L1DLkjLWXtjY37YwUettajmCzNlZOx55n9SO68MRu8nlgoBp04uhkNRY91ZAKyAB3jiqzoOvvR_gezBwHw5hrReb8sbz4WMeiA4frD8OmZkr-5MrbJnP-9Ziu6Cg8HA6rKZgBeH_urMKS6KFmYgfw5lGfaWQ5LJIU11McRXOui2bKP9Y0hmcnYbC_VG6fHGBHkvjks3oHpROfJzQ9QVoriXpxMHgGlYIGzudTn5bIYew5cq6lvJuwZMtYOOZ1pmpzOHgFNy5vuGkD0d_zKNWm-dwDQegb8Xb9lFJHdNOVnmiJctBeMFplo7pQnb0kJhVFpab63383OsBpfZyKw7kQf9L93zIS1vsKa5Rmw8oCfopWfD4AdAME8c5JutkNmTddMsHEClB7D7bUNzfZIWohjwT6U2IovMHv4qslVoC0IsDfML0QvK5M-rUrxPy4dEJEOpuQsWxBnk1mJfeD7dKDQHByFQ4q3RsG3gByopRsOJY92QF5O8_CENh22BCBoTqTHJnql7M370_f830XEhAic0laDzMvqlRhtKO5I7U103zCO9RIgQKybJD