{"type":"message","id":"9e667c64","parentId":"f61f4289","timestamp":"2026-03-26T13:24:49.785Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9QPRxwCvpNkmBEHwwmwiuvHT|fc_0142f9a21f5351e00169c533a1100c819bbd07425c7e11e40b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nimport subprocess\nimport sys\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nWORKSPACE = Path.home() / \".openclaw\" / \"workspace\"\nREPORT_DIR = WORKSPACE / \"research\" / \"reports\"\nHEALTH_SCRIPT = WORKSPACE / \"scripts\" / \"generate_investment_research_mainline_health.py\"\n\n\ndef today_tag() -> str:\n    return datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n\n\ndef load_json(path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    return json.loads(path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n\n\ndef run_health() -> tuple[dict[str, Any], Path, Path]:\n    proc = subprocess.run([sys.executable, str(HEALTH_SCRIPT)], cwd=str(WORKSPACE), capture_output=True, text=True, check=True)\n    lines = [line.strip() for line in proc.stdout.splitlines() if line.strip()]\n    md_path = Path(lines[0]) if lines else REPORT_DIR / f\"investment_research_mainline_health_{today_tag()}.md\"\n    json_path = Path(lines[1]) if len(lines) > 1 else REPORT_DIR / f\"investment_research_mainline_health_{today_tag()}.json\"\n    payload = load_json(json_path)\n    return payload, md_path, json_path\n\n\ndef build_summary(payload: dict[str, Any], md_path: Path, json_path: Path) -> str:\n    base = payload.get(\"alert_message\") or \"🩺 量化投研主链巡检：UNKNOWN\"\n    return \"\\n\".join([\n        base,\n        f\"- 健康报告：`{md_path}`\",\n        f\"- 健康JSON：`{json_path}`\",\n    ])\n\n\ndef exit_code(overall: str) -> int:\n    if overall == \"OK\":\n        return 0\n    if overall == \"WARN\":\n        return 10\n    if overall == \"ALERT\":\n        return 20\n    return 30\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    payload, md_path, json_path = run_health()\n    print(build_summary(payload, md_path, json_path))\n    raise SystemExit(exit_code(payload.get(\"overall_status\", \"UNKNOWN\")))\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774531489776}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b1e6929","parentId":"9e667c64","timestamp":"2026-03-26T13:24:49.796Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_mdlw7TZMfl48b1LnztMNuehU|fc_0142f9a21f5351e00169c533a11020819b9c3ef6250382de30","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 🌙 来福投研会｜夜间总览\n\n| 项目 | 当前值 |\n|---|---|\n| 审计状态 | PASS |\n| 盘前强检 | FULL_HALT |\n| 风险状态 | 偏防守 |\n| 年化/回撤/夏普 | 55.07 / 24.89 / 2.794 |\n\n**夜间研究重点**\n- 夜间研究优先延展明日观察主题：暂无。\n- 此时更适合做主线/分歧/风险偏好研究，而不是讨论可执行买价。\n- 若角色观点冲突明显，应先形成分歧清单，再决定次日是否提高会商强度。\n\n**观察池**\n- 暂无\n\n**卖出/减仓复核**\n- 当前策略未触发卖出/减仓复核。\n\n**持仓预览**\n- 002025.SZ 航天电器\n- 002565.SZ 顺灏股份\n- 300342.SZ 天银机电\n- 002025.SZ 航天电器\n- 002565.SZ 顺灏股份\n\n**近期成交预览**\n- 暂无\n\n**角色摘要**\n- 🌍 宏观研究员：📋 输入边界\n- 🏭 行业研究员：📋 输入边界\n- 📊 量化分析师：📋 输入边界\n- 💰 巴菲特分身：📋 输入边界\n\n**数据源策略**\n- 状态：offhours_guarded\n- 主源：yfinance\n- 次源：web_free_news_sources\n- 确认源：暂无\n- 判定说明：system_gate_warning:precheck_status=FULL_HALT; health_probe:offhours_guarded\n- 模拟盘快照：`-` | 新鲜度=`-` | 暂无\n- 实时健康：`offhours_guarded` | THS状态=`fallback` | THS命中/回退/失败=`0` / `3` / `0`\n- THS 摘要：THS 本地实时行情出现回退，检测 3，THS 命中 0，回退 3\n- 降级后动作：\n  - 切换到observe_defensive\n  - 停止输出可执行倾向\n  - 触发临时会商监控告警\n  - 在chief broadcast中提示数据源异常\n\n**主链快照**\n- 08:50晨报：`-` | 最近成功：`-`\n- 稳定策略：`-` | 年化/回撤/夏普：`-` / `-` / `-`\n- 回测队列：`-` | 运行中：`-` | 已纳入稳定策略：`-`\n\n**导出入口**\n- 持仓明细：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_paper_holdings_20260326.csv`\n- 成交明细：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_paper_trades_20260326.csv`\n- 交易建议卡：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_trade_card_night_20260326.md`\n- 首席总览：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_chief_dashboard_night_20260326.md`\n\n> 首席研究员结论：夜间研究以深挖逻辑、梳理分歧和明日主题为主，继续保持偏防守。\n> 当前非交易时段/非交易日，不提供可执行买价，只保留方向、预算和触发条件。\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774531489785}}
