d.py. It’s probably best to mention file paths, while keeping things straightforward for the user. I should also explain why the warning \\\"一直发策略守卫警告\\\" is a recurring issue due to crontab scheduling and a stale index. There were also more serious warnings on 3/25, indicating a halt state not being properly inherited.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Clarifying guard warnings**\\n\\nThe guard's function is working as intended. As of 3/26, critical warnings disappeared, leaving only stale CSV issues, which suggests the guard has effectively reduced severity. One warning in the evening reports indicates precheck is at FULL_HALT, with the data health off-hours guarded, leading to a downgrade for protection. There are two \\\"guard\\\" types causing alerts. I can explain that the logs reflect the latter due to different scheduled tasks reporting the same state. It's not a sign of new problems each time.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Suggesting alert improvements**\\n\\nI think it would be a good idea to suggest some improvements for the alert system. Specifically, I should consider deduplicating alerts so that users only receive notifications on status changes or critical issues. This way, we can reduce the noise in the reports and make it easier for everyone to focus on the really important updates. Keeping alerts relevant and targeted could really enhance the user experience!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_wPYFkCMdV16Nuqrp6zbXxJLS|fc_0142f9a21f5351e00169c5341510bc819ba23454170c4c78ef","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"nl -ba /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/run_tester_scheduled_guard.py | sed -n '20,140p' && printf '\\n---LATEST-MD---\\n' && nl -ba /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/tester_scheduled_guard_latest.md | sed -n '1,40p' && printf '\\n---LOG---\\n' && nl -ba /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/tester_guard.log | tail -n 40 && printf '\\n---PRECHECK---\\n' && nl -ba /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/auto_premarket_precheck_20260326.json | sed -n '1,80p'","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":120},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"nl -ba /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/run_tester_scheduled_guard.py | sed -n '20,140p' && printf '\\\\n---LATEST-MD---\\\\n' && nl -ba /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/tester_scheduled_guard_latest.md | sed -n '1,40p' && printf '\\\\n---LOG---\\\\n' && nl -ba /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/tester_guard.log | tail -n 40 && printf '\\\\n---PRECHECK---\\\\n' && nl -ba /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/auto_premarket_precheck_20260326.json | sed -n '1,80p'\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\",\"timeout\":120}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":82632,"output":727,"cacheRead":32256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115615,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774531569177,"responseId":"resp_0142f9a21f5351e00169c533fefe44819bbf6438989e0b420c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c4de6ee","parentId":"1c71eb9e","timestamp":"2026-03-26T13:26:46.824Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_wPYFkCMdV16Nuqrp6zbXxJLS|fc_0142f9a21f5351e00169c5341510bc819ba23454170c4c78ef","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"20\tdef append_issue(issues: list[dict[str, Any]], severity: str, code: str, detail: str) -> None:\n    21\t    issues.append({'severity': severity, 'code': code, 'detail': detail})\n    22\t\n    23\t\n    24\tdef main() -> None:\n    25\t    date_tag = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n    26\t    runtime = load_json(QUANT_REPORT_DIR / 'runtime_risk_state_latest.json')\n    27\t    report = load_json(QUANT_REPORT_DIR / f'today_stock_strategy_report_{date_tag}.json')\n    28\t    if not report:\n    29\t        report = load_json(QUANT_REPORT_DIR / 'today_stock_strategy_report_latest.json')\n    30\t    event_watch = load_json(REPORT_DIR / f'investment_research_event_watch_{date_tag}.json')\n    31\t\n    32\t    issues: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    33\t\n    34\t    latest_runtime = runtime.get('latest_runtime') or {}\n    35\t    report_trade_date = str(report.get('trade_date') or '').replace('-', '')\n    36\t    runtime_date = str(runtime.get('date_tag') or '')\n    37\t    report_mode = str(report.get('risk_mode') or '')\n    38\t    runtime_mode = str(latest_runtime.get('mode') or '')\n    39\t\n    40\t    if runtime and report:\n    41\t        if runtime_date == date_tag and report_trade_date == date_tag:\n    42\t            if runtime_mode and report_mode and runtime_mode != report_mode:\n    43\t                append_issue(issues, 'critical', 'runtime_report_mode_mismatch', f'runtime={runtime_mode}, report={report_mode}')\n    44\t            if latest_runtime.get('halt_new_buy') != report.get('halt_new_buy'):\n    45\t                append_issue(issues, 'critical', 'runtime_report_halt_mismatch', f\"runtime={latest_runtime.get('halt_new_buy')} report={report.get('halt_new_buy')}\")\n    46\t            if latest_runtime.get('market_breadth') != report.get('market_breadth'):\n    47\t                append_issue(issues, 'high', 'runtime_report_breadth_mismatch', f\"runtime={latest_runtime.get('market_breadth')} report={report.get('market_breadth')}\")\n    48\t\n    49\t    # halt 状态下模拟盘不应仍保留当日新增买入\n    50\t    if report_trade_date == date_tag and bool(report.get('halt_new_buy')):\n    51\t        for profile in ['defensive','balanced','aggressive']:\n    52\t            acc = load_json(QUANT_REPORT_DIR / f'paper_{profile}_account_v1_{date_tag}.json')\n    53\t            if acc:\n    54\t                buys = int(acc.get('today_buy_count') or 0)\n    55\t                if buys > 0:\n    56\t                    append_issue(issues, 'critical', f'paper_{profile}_buy_under_halt', f'today_buy_count={buys}')\n    57\t\n    58\t    # 事件监控链是否仍引用旧口径\n    59\t    if event_watch:\n    60\t        cur = event_watch.get('current') or {}\n    61\t        pe = cur.get('paper_execution_status') or {}\n    62\t        source = str(pe.get('source') or '')\n    63\t        if runtime_date == date_tag and source not in {'runtime_risk_state_latest', 'strategy_report'}:\n    64\t            append_issue(issues, 'high', 'event_watch_not_using_runtime', f'source={source}')\n    65\t        if runtime_mode and str(pe.get('mode') or '') != runtime_mode:\n    66\t            append_issue(issues, 'high', 'event_watch_mode_mismatch', f\"event_watch={pe.get('mode')} runtime={runtime_mode}\")\n    67\t\n    68\t\n    69\t    # ===== 深层防控：早盘 halt 延续一致性检查 =====\n    70\t    # 如果上一个交易日收盘后 intraday recheck 为 halt，\n    71\t    # 而今日仍有新买入订单通过 → 说明早盘风控未能继承 halt，是严重缺陷\n    72\t    import glob as _glob\n    73\t\n    74\t    # ===== CSV 指数数据新鲜度检查 =====\n    75\t    # 如果今日是交易日，但 CSV 最后更新日期 < 今日，\n    76\t    # 说明早盘用 T-1 数据生成订单，任何基于 index_ret_pct 的 halt 判断都不可靠\n    77\t    csv_index_path = Path(\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis/index_000852_SH.csv\")\n    78\t    if csv_index_path.exists():\n    79\t        import pandas as _pd\n    80\t        try:\n    81\t            df_idx = _pd.read_csv(csv_index_path)\n    82\t            last_csv_date = int(df_idx.iloc[-1][\"trade_date\"])\n    83\t            today_int = int(datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\"))\n    84\t            if last_csv_date < today_int:\n    85\t                append_issue(\n    86\t                    issues,\n    87\t                    \"high\",\n    88\t                    \"csv_index_data_stale\",\n    89\t                    f\"CSV 指数数据陈旧（{last_csv_date} < {today_int}），早盘 halt 判断不可靠\",\n    90\t                )\n    91\t        except Exception:\n    92\t            pass\n    93\t    if date_tag:\n    94\t        prev_dt = str(int(date_tag) - 1) if len(date_tag) == 8 else None\n    95\t        if prev_dt:\n    96\t            prev_rt_files = sorted(_glob.glob(str(QUANT_REPORT_DIR / f\"intraday_risk_recheck_{prev_dt}_*.json\")))\n    97\t            if prev_rt_files:\n    98\t                prev_rt = json.loads(open(prev_rt_files[-1], encoding=\"utf-8\").read())\n    99\t                prev_halt = bool(prev_rt.get(\"latest_runtime\", {}).get(\"halt_new_buy\"))\n   100\t                if prev_halt:\n   101\t                    # 上日 halt，检查今日是否有买\n   102\t                    for profile in [\"defensive\", \"balanced\", \"aggressive\"]:\n   103\t                        acc = load_json(QUANT_REPORT_DIR / f\"paper_{profile}_account_v1_{date_tag}.json\")\n   104\t                        if acc:\n   105\t                            buys = int(acc.get(\"today_buy_count\") or 0)\n   106\t                            if buys > 0:\n   107\t                                # 进一步确认买的是今日新开仓（非持仓维护）\n   108\t                                holdings = acc.get(\"holdings\") or {}\n   109\t                                if isinstance(holdings, dict):\n   110\t                                    from datetime import timedelta\n   111\t                                    open_dates = [v.get(\"open_date\", \"\") for v in holdings.values() if isinstance(v, dict)]\n   112\t                                    today_str = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n   113\t                                    is_new_position = today_str in str(open_dates)\n   114\t                                    if is_new_position:\n   115\t                                        append_issue(\n   116\t                                            issues,\n   117\t                                            \"critical\",\n   118\t                                            f\"prev_halt_buy_through_{profile}\",\n   119\t                                            f\"前日 halt 延续，但 {profile} 今日仍有新增买={buys}（应被早盘风控阻断）\",\n   120\t                                        )\n   121\t\n   122\t    # 深层阻断检查链是否持续接通\n   123\t    deep_guard = load_json(QUANT_REPORT_DIR / 'paper_sim_deep_guard_check_latest.json')\n   124\t    if deep_guard:\n   125\t        if str(deep_guard.get('status') or '') not in {'PASS', 'WARN'}:\n   126\t            append_issue(issues, 'high', 'paper_sim_deep_guard_not_ready', f\"status={deep_guard.get('status')}\")\n   127\t    else:\n   128\t        append_issue(issues, 'high', 'paper_sim_deep_guard_missing', 'paper_sim_deep_guard_check_latest.json missing')\n   129\t\n   130\t    status = 'PASS' if not issues else ('ALERT' if any(i['severity']=='critical' for i in issues) else 'WARN')\n   131\t    payload = {\n   132\t        'generated_at': datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'),\n   133\t        'date_tag': date_tag,\n   134\t        'status': status,\n   135\t        'issue_count': len(issues),\n   136\t        'issues': issues,\n   137\t        'inputs': {\n   138\t            'runtime_state': str(QUANT_REPORT_DIR / 'runtime_risk_state_latest.json'),\n   139\t            'strategy_report': str(QUANT_REPORT_DIR / f'today_stock_strategy_report_{date_tag}.json'),\n   140\t            'event_watch': str(REPORT_DIR / f'investment_research_event_watch_{date_tag}.json'),\n\n---LATEST-MD---\n     1\t# Tester 定时检验\n     2\t\n     3\t- 生成时间：2026-03-26 16:35:01\n     4\t- 状态：`WARN`\n     5\t- 问题数：`1`\n     6\t\n     7\t## 问题列表\n     8\t- [high] `csv_index_data_stale`：CSV 指数数据陈旧（20260325 < 20260326），早盘 halt 判断不可靠\n\n---LOG---\n   195\t  \"issue_count\": 3,\n   196\t  \"latest_json\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/tester_scheduled_guard_latest.json\",\n   197\t  \"latest_md\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/tester_scheduled_guard_latest.md\"\n   198\t}\n   199\t{\n   200\t  \"status\": \"WARN\",\n   201\t  \"issue_count\": 2,\n   202\t  \"latest_json\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/tester_scheduled_guard_latest.json\",\n   203\t  \"latest_md\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/tester_scheduled_guard_latest.md\"\n   204\t}\n   205\t{\n   206\t  \"status\": \"WARN\",\n   207\t  \"issue_count\": 2,\n   208\t  \"latest_json\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/tester_scheduled_guard_latest.json\",\n   209\t  \"latest_md\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/tester_scheduled_guard_latest.md\"\n   210\t}\n   211\t{\n   212\t  \"status\": \"WARN\",\n   213\t  \"issue_count\": 2,\n   214\t  \"latest_json\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/tester_scheduled_guard_latest.json\",\n   215\t  \"latest_md\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/tester_scheduled_guard_latest.md\"\n   216\t}\n   217\t{\n   218\t  \"status\": \"WARN\",\n   219\t  \"issue_count\": 2,\n   220\t  \"latest_json\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/tester_scheduled_guard_latest.json\",\n   221\t  \"latest_md\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/tester_scheduled_guard_latest.md\"\n   222\t}\n   223\t{\n   224\t  \"status\": \"WARN\",\n   225\t  \"issue_count\": 2,\n   226\t  \"latest_json\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/te