sts that outputs should use Chinese terms like 强提醒 instead of English ones like FULL_HALT or WARN. I could audit these scripts using grep to find common English statuses and potentially create a report to patch the central scripts.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我先直接改，不空讲：先把 ACTIVE_TASK 切到“用户可见输出全面中文化检查”，然后扫描当前最容易对你暴露英文的生成/推送脚本，先出一轮可落地修正。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0142f9a21f5351e00169c5381160ec819baa3832c4668ba3d1\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_U32eRRL38fNNz88SXg1g5W2V|fc_0142f9a21f5351e00169c53811aa14819ba79abaf2a84953bc","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_TEMPLATE.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_TEMPLATE.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_kVAofMLOHJWcJNzAOdQ5PT7u|fc_0142f9a21f5351e00169c53811aa28819b898f2e97fc8abadb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/active_task_cli.py show --path /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":60},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/active_task_cli.py show --path /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\",\"timeout\":60}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_Oc4vPzloR0t7Kt67HFxKiwyc|fc_0142f9a21f5351e00169c53811aa30819b9ed5d3200504b54a","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/highest_priority_execution_queue_20260319.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/highest_priority_execution_queue_20260319.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":86026,"output":730,"cacheRead":45568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132324,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774532574058,