{"type":"message","id":"f9653f18","parentId":"a5978d12","timestamp":"2026-03-26T13:43:46.117Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Oc4vPzloR0t7Kt67HFxKiwyc|fc_0142f9a21f5351e00169c53811aa30819b9ed5d3200504b54a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 最高层级任务连续执行清单（2026-03-19）\n\n> 规则：每完成一个最小验收件，立即进入下一个；除非出现阻断或用户改优先级，否则不得停在“已交付、未继续执行”的状态。\n\n## 当前最高层级任务\n量化系统 P0/P1 漏洞清单 + 自动检验补强计划\n\n## 执行队列\n\n### 已完成\n- [x] P0/P1 规则文件：`quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/quant_p0_p1_guard_rules_v1.json`\n- [x] P0 自动审计脚本：`scripts/run_quant_p0_audit.py`\n- [x] tester 定时检验：`scripts/run_tester_scheduled_guard.py` + cron\n- [x] 模拟盘主链入口前阻断：`run_paper_trading_profiles_auto_v1.sh`\n- [x] 账户结果 guard：`scripts/prewrite_paper_guard.py`\n- [x] 下午自动重跑强制刷新链完整自检：`scripts/run_intraday_risk_recheck.py` + `scripts/cron_intraday_rebuild_paper_profiles_v1.sh` + `research/reports/intraday_recovery_automation_20260319.md`\n- [x] 个股实时前置门禁并入下午自动重跑主链：`scripts/stock_level_realtime_gate.py` + `scripts/check_stock_level_gate_chain.py` + `research/reports/stock_level_gate_chain_check_latest.md`\n- [x] 错误买入自动纠偏/回滚第一版：`scripts/apply_paper_rollback.py` + `research/reports/paper_rollback_apply_20260319.md`\n- [x] 多源实时宽度兜底：`scripts/intraday_market_breadth.py` + `research/reports/intraday_breadth_fallback_progress_20260319.md`\n\n### 已完成（续 2026-03-19 22:50）\n- [x] THS/TDX 统一路由接入主链\n  - stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py: DataFetcherManager (THS→Pytdx→Efinance→腾讯降级) ✅ 实测 002920 ¥113.75\n  - intraday_market_gate.py: 统一路由 + Tencent 降级 ✅ 实测 上证-1.39% 深证-2.02%\n  - intraday_market_breadth.py: 三源兜底 ✅ 实测 472涨/4499跌/9.5%\n  - commit: d499de8, 8743e3b, 083b938\n\n### 下一批（按顺序继续）\n（队列全部完成，P0/P1 漏洞清单已全部落地）\n\n## 强制执行规则\n1. 每轮只能选择一个 `[ ]` 项作为本轮最小验收件。\n2. 完成一个后，立即把下一个 `[ ]` 项升级为当前执行项，不得停留在空档。\n3. 若本轮无新增产物，汇报只能写：`无新增产物`。\n4. 若本轮修的是旁支，必须写：`旁支有新增，主任务无新增产物`。\n5. 若出现阻断，必须写清：阻断点 / 缺什么 / 为什么当前无法继续。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774532626104}}
