{"type":"message","id":"3e05166e","parentId":"285ab63d","timestamp":"2026-03-26T13:55:42.603Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_dSXOg6fWiRfSyRQoQXBqMlDv|fc_0142f9a21f5351e00169c53addbdf4819ba1ea9c330ee0e676","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nfrom report_io import atomic_write_json, atomic_write_text\n\nWORKSPACE = Path.home() / \".openclaw\" / \"workspace\"\nREPORT_DIR = WORKSPACE / \"research\" / \"reports\"\n\n\ndef today_tag() -> str:\n    return datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n\n\ndef load_json(path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    return json.loads(path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n\n\ndef control_tower_path() -> Path:\n    path = REPORT_DIR / f\"investment_research_control_tower_{today_tag()}.json\"\n    if not path.exists():\n        raise FileNotFoundError(str(path))\n    return path\n\n\ndef truncate_list(items: list[str], limit: int = 5) -> str:\n    if not items:\n        return \"暂无\"\n    return \"\\n\".join(f\"- {item}\" for item in items[:limit])\n\n\ndef yes_no(value: Any) -> str:\n    if value is True:\n        return \"是\"\n    if value is False:\n        return \"否\"\n    if value is None or value == \"\":\n        return \"-\"\n    return str(value)\n\n\ndef cn_status(value: Any) -> str:\n    mapping = {\n        \"OK\": \"正常\",\n        \"WARN\": \"预警\",\n        \"ERROR\": \"错误\",\n        \"PASS\": \"通过\",\n        \"ALERT\": \"告警\",\n        \"healthy\": \"健康\",\n        \"watch_guarded\": \"警戒观察\",\n        \"offhours_guarded\": \"非交易时段观察\",\n        \"degraded\": \"降级\",\n        \"triggered\": \"已触发\",\n        \"normal\": \"正常\",\n        \"cautious\": \"谨慎\",\n        \"halt\": \"暂停\",\n        \"halt_new_positions\": \"暂停新增仓位\",\n        \"observe_defensive\": \"防守观察\",\n        \"PENDING_TODAY\": \"待今日晨报\",\n        \"STALE\": \"状态过期\",\n        \"PUSH_FAILED\": \"推送失败\",\n        \"GENERATION_FAILED\": \"生成失败\",\n        \"DEADLINE_MISSED\": \"超时未完成\",\n        \"SKIP_NON_TRADING_DAY\": \"非交易日跳过\",\n        \"MISSING\": \"缺失\",\n        \"ok\": \"正常\",\n        \"fallback\": \"已回退\",\n        \"failed\": \"部分失败\",\n        \"unavailable\": \"不可用\",\n        \"unknown\": \"未知\",\n        \"fresh\": \"今日已刷新\",\n        \"pending_today_refresh\": \"待今日刷新\",\n        \"stale\": \"已过期\",\n        \"mixed\": \"日期混杂\",\n        \"missing\": \"缺失\",\n    }\n    if value is None or value == \"\":\n        return \"-\"\n    return mapping.get(str(value), str(value))\n\n\ndef cn_text(text: Any) -> str:\n    if text is None or text == \"\":\n        return \"-\"\n    s = str(text)\n    replacements = {\n        \"market_breadth\": \"市场宽度\",\n        \"source_price_divergence\": \"数据源价差分歧\",\n        \"account_sync_age\": \"账户同步时延\",\n        \"observe_defensive\": \"防守观察\",\n        \"halt_new_positions\": \"暂停新增仓位\",\n        \"watch_guarded\": \"警戒观察\",\n        \"offhours_guarded\": \"非交易时段观察\",\n        \"healthy\": \"健康\",\n        \"degraded\": \"降级\",\n        \"triggered\": \"已触发\",\n        \"FULL_HALT\": \"全市场暂停新增\",\n        \"BUY_HALT\": \"暂停买入\",\n        \"normal\": \"正常\",\n        \"cautious\": \"谨慎\",\n        \"normal模式\": \"正常模式\",\n        \"public_source_divergence>\": \"公开网页源存在价差分歧 > \",\n        \"BUY\": \"买入\",\n        \"SELL\": \"卖出\",\n    }\n    for old, new in replacements.items():\n        s = s.replace(old, new)\n    return s\n\n\ndef build_card(payload: dict[str, Any]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    latest_status = payload.get(\"latest_status\", {})\n    watchlist = payload.get(\"watchlist\", [])[:5]\n    watchlist_reason = payload.get(\"watchlist_reason\") or \"暂无\"\n    holdings = payload.get(\"holdings_preview\", [])[:5]\n\n[186 more lines in file. Use offset=121 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774533342586}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ab4e6c9","parentId":"3e05166e","timestamp":"2026-03-26T13:55:53.670Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering code updates**\n\nI'm evaluating the need to patch the cn_status mapping in control_tower.py and control_tower_broadcast. It might be a good idea to add WARN and off-hours options, especially since control_tower.py already handles off-hours. I could also explore adding a WARN mapping, which seems feasible. Additionally, I'm contemplating whether to patch control_tower and possibly the mainline health with an unknown status, though that might not be necessary after all.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0142f9a21f5351e00169c53ae4f738819bbebaef91627c8fd6\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpxTro1rV81QKjwUySQ66r5vzOh5wb11EOPjm1ksw38UhBZ8oSlCz0Od9QmX9fpQNj30IosnxFzbICyK-8bHGMUWvGY2KTUiF_sh8WYe0bcK0McavD6lPFMsjT4qeBD6UExxZT_bbe9T210djXIn39iA1r0mAcJ67oL_i23qGuw0J5_ZLQARW8xqC9ocyha6cIi9OCHt3KiEVtOCj470GflP4jpCdBveVxyrtcbNoy7sPKo-xn5cX2U6CJyOn6G5KkFM4g9fXi6y529P2awjon6xXOT8tGE6l-BQrgIPAoem0lGrQfT2gqobOvolDxHAZNOZUgO3Vq7k1YARP3Vt6h98dGCQzcec18hw6BTy5j0hd4ahkFW7OoNCDB6QzyHckXpOLNFDst2TtxDwboYrrU6t9BFNbNqlUFpP464SG3HPCH0gr4IqXTwPZf0WQFUXT_WSM1669LrZ5NdJmfFK7naiJPnLs_hbTUv5QkeaTfrIgrFhVoloZU7l6QhrTLINOBJHgFTk4a7KLfWZEJb7ninZD8pR6qQ7hKEVmJ0p6OOg2uItBp9oqU37cJZ77ze5z5WNDkHEJLubDSWzLqIeFqdC2Ok_-oT3z7oSz_GPI2cFGUkesRnUFSRXrg_cJX_TyRJMJ8eCUdbRqbkx3Twd3d2PNvPBjB1ZVuhxg2_jXfTVSKE4PKQMBzWg874VjI9wACnANOmz0rCoWiNuIb6p7mCLnfGxPCgLGwMqAbg8K8aPLd2Tjt23KaPAo_aatM-riD-O-e3zGLzcl-zR1Be4KGTtg6m7sOWqDSVZtZ0H9J7sjEQNnlLuJmrfznnsWzdJcz0aCCTGG3uOV7Ut9cDzzGlSxRUyLuLl06V8BrBKGv1ZkqoWaV3pEHFE8gbTXLnsVHMvcOWtNf9urgyPI_tnfj5Y4fDvtNauJz1HPwByZqW8ZASp67AQW8TwWTYmDo9rNY2R2E54481JGSGjaNuRR-ujxCa6eldKQEB9_ncSjnzUR2nly3Jdj9F_67J3c7LKebHmEvDi1fZWa3x3QvhC3a2-P2a5__LOUWxkrq7iHCcMn-_hU1lZmXNp5hgTy3u7Yh_zRquo7agcu0r9-voJraf5J_W1QaiHI_5DiGySB7re3wvZZcmSzFkL3r-s27_snLnFx1UyKLsj9BckKrnGVLzI0VavTvXGrP5iTik-hpsVEGb5yECD